highlights.text: Perunggu has the most spots on Viral Songs Indonesia. “Aku Ada Untukmu” is the highest at #22.
“Luxurious x Be Your Girl - Jersey - Slowed” by VIP and archangel is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Indonesia at #56.
“About You” by The 1975 has been on Viral Songs Indonesia the longest, at 392 days straight.
“WRONG” by Chris Grey is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Indonesia, up 15 spots at #55.
